ine of the business. A lot of our traffic is organic, and our SEO needs to be spot-on. You'll oversee all aspects of SEO for all of our products and domains. As the Sr. SEO Manager, you'll work across all teams to develop and implement strategies to improve online visibility, rankings, conversions, and ROI by optimizing our content and website structure. We're an established company and have been in the market for 17+ years. Now, we need you to take it to the next level.",{"type":26,"tag":35,"props":966,"children":967},{},[968],{"type":32,"value":969},"What you'll do:",{"type":26,"tag":52,"props":971,"children":972},{},[973,978,983,988,993,998,1003,1008,1013],{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":974,"children":975},{},[976],{"type":32,"value":977},"Develop a holistic SEO strategy that grows organic search traffic and conversions and aligns with the overall company goals and priorities; execute the roadmap; and track performance.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":979,"children":980},{},[981],{"type":32,"value":982},"Proactively test, analyze, and make changes to product domains to ensure they are optimized for search engines and rank higher in the search results on major search engines (e.g., Google, Google Scholar, Bing).",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":984,"children":985},{},[986],{"type":32,"value":987},"Conduct regular website audits to identify areas for improvement and implement necessary changes.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":989,"children":990},{},[991],{"type":32,"value":992},"Contribute SEO expertise to the overall website strategy and collaborate with other departments within the company, such as Marketing, Sales, Business Development, Technology, and Product, to ensure content and overall Information Architecture drive relevant traffic by meeting search intent.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":994,"children":995},{},[996],{"type":32,"value":997},"Collaborate with the Engineering team to implement SEO-friendly technical changes (e.g., optimize for Web Vitals, add appropriate schema).",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":999,"children":1000},{},[1001],{"type":32,"value":1002},"Define, tune, execute, and capitalize on content gaps with our competitors, content growth, and content optimization opportunities.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1004,"children":1005},{},[1006],{"type":32,"value":1007},"Keep ahead of the newest SEO strategies, techniques, and best practices to improve our SEO strategies continuously.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1009,"children":1010},{},[1011],{"type":32,"value":1012},"Discover link opportunities through competitive backlink research via tools such as Majestic SEO, Ahrefs, Open Site Explorer, and SEM Rush.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1014,"children":1015},{},[1016],{"type":32,"value":1017},"Monitor and report key performance indicators such as indexing, rankings, backlinks, and SERP click-through rates.",{"type":26,"tag":27,"props":1019,"children":1020},{"id":88},[1021],{"type":32,"value":91},{"type":26,"tag":93,"props":1023,"children":1024},{},[1025,1029,1033,1037],{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1026,"children":1027},{},[1028],{"type":32,"value":338},{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1030,"children":1031},{},[1032],{"type":32,"value":343},{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1034,"children":1035},{},[1036],{"type":32,"value":115},{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1038,"children":1039},{},[1040],{"type":32,"value":357},{"type":26,"tag":27,"props":1042,"children":1043},{"id":123},[1044],{"type":32,"value":126},{"type":26,"tag":52,"props":1046,"children":1047},{},[1048,1052,1057,1062,1067,1072,1077,1082,1087,1092,1097,1102,1107,1112],{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1049,"children":1050},{},[1051],{"type":32,"value":134},{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1053,"children":1054},{},[1055],{"type":32,"value":1056},"8+ years of full-time hands-on SEO experience.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1058,"children":1059},{},[1060],{"type":32,"value":1061},"3+ years of full-time hands-on SEO Manager/Lead experience.",{"type":26,"tag":56,"props":1063,"children":1064},{},[1065]